STAT ENHANCEMENT

Darkwind has the capability of temporarily increasing a player's 
abilities without actually changing the character.  The functions to do 
this are  add_<stat>(int)  where <stat> is the ability you want to 
increase and int is the amount to boost it.
This document contains Darkwind's policy on stat-enhancing items.


ALL stat-enhancing items are EXCEPTIONAL.  (See wizhelp 4.14 (uniques).)

No permanent item may increase a stat more than 4 points.  A permanent 
item that increases a stat more than 2 points must be created unique.  Those
that increase a stat by 4 are to be considered very powerful, and should
only be found guarded by some of the most powerful, legendary creatures
of the land.

No temporary item may increase a stat more than 8 points.  A temporary 
item that increases a stat more than 5 points must be created unique.  
(Once it is used up, the item can be created again, but this will prevent 
guild stockpiles and such.)  NOTE:  anything with a duration longer than
five minutes will not be considered temporary.

Multiple stat-enhancing items may be used concurrently, even if they 
affect the same stat.  The old Ogre Gaunlets and Giant Girdle combination 
is an example.  (But see next paragraph.)

Players must NOT be able to use multiple copies of an item to stack their 
bonuses.  You cannot have two Amulets Of Beauty worn at the same time to 
get a larger CHR bonus, for example.  If you have a temporary item that 
enhances a stat, you must put a marker on the player so that they cannot 
use that item again until it wears off.  (There is an example of this 
type of item in /open/wizards/antcrusher/tome_l_i.c.)

Bonus stats may NEVER carry over from one login to the next.

Any weapon that enhances stats must be created unique.  Period.

An armor that enhances stats may not also be exceptional for high armor
class or resistance.  Enhancing stats is enough.

*************************IMPORTANT*********************************
IF YOU GIVE A BONUS TO A PLAYER FOR SAY "WEARING" AN ITEM, YOU MUST
ENSURE THAT WHEN THE ITEM IS REMOVED, THE BONUS IS ALSO REMOVED!!!!
*******************************************************************


